bug.short_desc: jsFiddle links lead to data-url content in jsFiddle on iPad

long_desc.thetext: Clicking on a jsFiddle link on iPad lead to a strange behavior. The content of the three editor panes seems to have something like base64 encoded data in it. But the result seems to be ok.
